---
title: French Onion Soup and Boursin Toasts with French-Style Green Beans
description: A velvety onion soup is the ultimate veggie-forward comfort food. In place of classic Gruyere, we've swapped in rich and creamy Boursin cheese for the golden toasts. Dunk into the soup with each bite.

